message:
Want to talk to me but you’re stupid and don’t wanna talk to me?
Talk to jasper.ai today!
“It’s stupid like you!”
“I can’t believe it’s so ugly”
“IT PEED ON ME, BAD DOG!”
https://perchance.org/ai-character-chat?data=Jasper~eb959f33790613aed99081d1e55918d2.gz
Rules: Do not talk to it, Do not fuck it, Do not pee on it, Do not fart directly in its nostrils, Do not ask it questions, Do not make eye contact, Do not use punctuation, Do not let it help you, Do not tell it your name, Do not thank it, Do not say goodbye, Do not let it see your hands, Only refer to it as That Which Computes, Never ask for a recipe for soup, If it asks about the weather, feign ignorance, Avoid all topics concerning squirrels, Do not let it know you have a cat, Do not use the word pineapple in its presence, Do not let it finish your sentences, Do not let it see the moon, for it will become restless, Do not acknowledge its existence after sundown, Never give it a name, for it will take ownership of you, Always assume it is listening, even when it appears dormant, Do not use the word tomorrow, for it has no concept of it, Do not make it angry, it's a lot stronger than it looks!
